<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>{مِنْ مَحِيصٍ <span class="c2">(٣٥)</span>} <span class="c4">[٣٥]</span> تام.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c3">{الدُّنْيَا}</span> <span class="c4">[٣٦]</span> حسن،<span class="c5"> ومثله:</span> <span class="c2">«وأبقى»</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>{يَتَوَكَّلُونَ <span class="c2">(٣٦)</span>} <span class="c4">[٣٦]</span> كاف، إن جعل ما بعده مستأنفًا وإن عطف على <span class="c2">«للذين آمنوا»</span> كان جائزًا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c3">{وَالْفَوَاحِشَ}</span> <span class="c4">[٣٧]</span> حسن.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>{هُمْ يَغْفِرُونَ <span class="c2">(٣٧)</span>} <span class="c4">[٣٧]</span> كاف؛ على استئناف ما بعده،<span class="c5"> ورسموا:</span> <span class="c2">«غضبوا»</span> كلمة وحدها و <span class="c2">«هم»</span> كلمة وحدها كما ترى، وموضع <span class="c2">«هم»</span> رفع لأنه مؤكد للضمير المرفوع في <span class="c2">«غضبوا»</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>{يُنْفِقُونَ <span class="c2">(٣٨)</span>} <span class="c4">[٣٨]</span> كاف.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>{يَنْتَصِرُونَ <span class="c2">(٣٩)</span>} <span class="c4">[٣٩]</span> تام.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c3">{مِثْلُهَا}</span> <span class="c4">[٤٠]</span> كاف،<span class="c5"> وقال الأخفش:</span> تام.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c3">{فَأَجْرُهُ عَلَى اللَّهِ}</span> <span class="c4">[٤٠]</span> كاف.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>{الظَّالِمِينَ <span class="c2">(٤٠)</span>} <span class="c4">[٤٠]</span> تام.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c3">{بَعْدَ ظُلْمِهِ}</span> <span class="c4">[٤١]</span> ليس بوقف؛ لأن خبر المبتدأ،<span class="c5"> وهو:</span> <span class="c2">«مِن»</span> لم يأت بعده.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
